thread.title_full: Yaniv & Associates, PC reviewed by Josh

author: Josh
title: Josh
text:
This firm got me my divorce in less than two months. Definitely worth the money.
The staff was extremely professional and polite. All emails or calls were answered within the hour.
If I were recommending this service to a friend I would recommend that they contact Britney and have her walk through the steps and timeline with them. She was really fantastic with helping me understand this complex process.
